{"tid":2351941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【故事分享】香港人會記住 唔會忘記","createTime":"2021-01-03T16:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T09:01:30.000Z","uid":231957,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8746f5ff274f8721a849bd0aa1a20c1fcb882038","tid":2351941,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:00:24.000Z","msg":"哩句野係＿大保護戰果時 有個的士佬講既<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;你明唔明 後生仔 我老啦 可能幫唔到手 但係 我一路聽住收音機 我都知哩件事係個政府唔啱&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;無論點都好 今晚香港人好團結 有需要幫忙既都會互相幫忙&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;政府做既野係唔啱架 我都知哩場仗應該點都輸 人地又有槍 又有刀 我地就得把遮&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n「但係唔緊要架 哩件事成件事 我地香港人都會記住 唔會忘記 就好似種左粒種子入我地個心度咁 哩成件事會永遠記係我地個腦中 等到有機會  我地一定會還返曬所有野比佢地」"},{"pid":"67e2358cfa24b3d3876492597889c883db5970cc","tid":2351941,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5a69b54d1fcb72b61f78099ff03a5921f87e80","tid":2351941,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe4aacd51a043e971a0f41df519bf763c8a3b5e","tid":2351941,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"